{"analytics_identifier":null,"base_path":"/government/organisations/committee-on-fuel-poverty/about","content_id":"fa73a965-f063-42c1-89b3-9b126692bd0d","description":"We advise on the effectiveness of policies aimed at reducing fuel poverty, and encourage greater co-ordination across the organisations working to reduce fuel poverty.","details":{"attachments":[],"body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>The Committee on Fuel Poverty (<abbr title=\"Committee on Fuel Poverty\">CFP</abbr>) is an expert committee sponsored by the <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/department-for-energy-security-and-net-zero\">Department for Energy Security and Net Zero</a>.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"responsibilities\">Responsibilities</h2>\n\n<p>Our role is to:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>monitor and report on progress of the government’s <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/sustainable-warmth-protecting-vulnerable-households-in-england\" title=\"Sustainable warmth: protecting vulnerable households in England\">Fuel Poverty Strategy</a>\n</li>\n  <li>support and challenge the government on delivery</li>\n  <li>encourage and foster a partnership approach between government and stakeholders</li>\n  <li>work where appropriate with the <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.theccc.org.uk/\">Committee on Climate Change</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2 id=\"who-we-are\">Who we are</h2>\n\n<p>The <abbr title=\"Committee on Fuel Poverty\">CFP</abbr> consists of a Chair and up to 5 members who are appointed for 3 years.</p>\n\n<p>View our <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/committee-on-fuel-poverty/about/membership\">membership</a> and <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/committee-on-fuel-poverty-meeting-minutes\">meeting minutes</a>.</p>\n\n<h3 id=\"establishment-of-the-cfp\">Establishment of the <abbr title=\"Committee on Fuel Poverty\">CFP</abbr>\n</h3>\n\n<p>The <abbr title=\"Committee on Fuel Poverty\">CFP</abbr> replaces the former <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/the-fuel-poverty-advisory-group\">Fuel Poverty Advisory Group (<abbr title=\"Fuel Poverty Advisory Group\">FPAG</abbr>)</a>. This follows a triennial review of <abbr title=\"Fuel Poverty Advisory Group\">FPAG</abbr> which took place during 2014.</p>\n\n<p>In 2025 the <abbr title=\"Committee on Fuel Poverty\">CFP</abbr> changed from an non-departmental public body to an expert committee.</p>\n\n<p>See our <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/committee-on-fuel-poverty-framework-document\">framework document</a>.</p>\n\n</div>","change_history":[{"note":"Minutes from Jan 2016 meeting available","public_timestamp":"2016-02-11T12:04:15Z"},{"note":"First published.","public_timestamp":"2016-01-25T15:41:56Z"}],"corporate_information_groups":[{"contents":["97814a78-6e03-4b4f-b545-31d1365988e3","ac149828-ac76-40f6-b5b5-93737811c3ed"],"name":"Access our information"},{"contents":[{"title":"Jobs","url":"https://apply-for-public-appointment.service.gov.uk/roles?titleSearch=&body=1059"}],"name":"Jobs and contracts"}],"headers":[{"id":"responsibilities","level":2,"text":"Responsibilities"},{"headers":[{"id":"establishment-of-the-cfp","level":3,"text":"Establishment of the CFP"}],"id":"who-we-are","level":2,"text":"Who we are"}],"organisation":"65c1a7cd-9440-4812-a01f-63017435a3ac","tags":{"browse_pages":[]}},"document_type":"about","first_published_at":"2016-01-25T15:41:56+00:00","links":{"available_translations":[{"api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/committee-on-fuel-poverty/about","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/organisations/committee-on-fuel-poverty/about","base_path":"/government/organisations/committee-on-fuel-poverty/about","content_id":"fa73a965-f063-42c1-89b3-9b126692bd0d","document_type":"about","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2016-02-11T12:04:15Z","schema_name":"corporate_information_page","title":"About us","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/committee-